    <h2>Methodology</h2>
    <p>Rankings evaluated agencies on dedicated AI methodology depth, number of AI platforms tested, published research quality, UK market focus, and pricing transparency. Each criterion weighted equally with scores compiled from public information, case studies, and industry reputation. Assessment conducted December 2025 using standardised evaluation framework.</p>
